# Project Context: all-in-one-frontend

## Code language

- **Generated code is always in English**, never in Portuguese: variable names, function names, comments, strings in the UI, log messages, and any other code or copy produced by the AI must be written in English, even when the user's instructions are in Portuguese.

## Stack

- **Framework**: Vue 3 (Composition API) + TypeScript
- **Build**: Vite 7
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4, CSS variables (slate base), tw-animate-css
- **UI**: shadcn-vue (New York style), Reka UI, Lucide icons
- **State**: Pinia
- **Routing**: Vue Router 4
- **HTTP**: Axios (client in `src/core/api/client.ts`; interceptor returns `response.data` and normalizes errors with `message`)

## Main structure (MVC Modular)

- **`src/core/`** — Infrastructure used by the whole app (no feature-specific logic).
  - `core/api/client.ts` — Axios instance; all module APIs import from here.
  - `core/lib/` — `utils.ts` (`cn()`), `format.ts` (dates, money).
  - `core/composables/` — e.g. `useTheme.ts`.
  - `core/router/index.ts` — single router; lazy-imports views from `@/modules/*/view/*`.
  - `core/stores/` — global stores only (e.g. counter); feature stores live in `modules/<name>/model/store.ts`.
- **`src/shared/`** — UI shared across modules.
  - `shared/components/ui/` — shadcn-vue components (Button, Card, Dialog, etc.).
  - `shared/components/AppSidebar.vue` — app sidebar.
  - `shared/layouts/` — e.g. `AuthenticatedLayout.vue`.
- **`src/modules/<module>/`** — One folder per feature; each has `model/` and optionally `view/`.
  - `model/` — API functions (import `api` from `@/core/api/client`), Pinia store if needed, types.
  - `view/` — Vue page components (routes reference them via `@/modules/<module>/view/...`).
  - Current modules: `auth`, `dashboard`, `accounts-payable`.
- **`src/assets/index.css`** — Global styles and theme.

## Imports (always use these paths)

- UI: `@/shared/components/ui/...`, `@/shared/components/AppSidebar.vue`, `@/shared/layouts/...`
- Core: `@/core/api/client`, `@/core/lib/utils`, `@/core/lib/format`, `@/core/composables/useTheme`, `@/core/router`
- Auth: `@/modules/auth/model/store`, `@/modules/auth/model/api`
- Other modules: `@/modules/<module>/model/...`, `@/modules/<module>/view/...`
- Do not use old paths: `@/components`, `@/views`, `@/api`, `@/stores`, `@/lib`, `@/composables`, `@/layouts` (they no longer exist).

## Aliases (`@/`)

- Tsconfig: `@/*` → `./src/*` (so `@/core/...`, `@/shared/...`, `@/modules/...` work).
- components.json (shadcn): `components` → `@/shared/components`, `ui` → `@/shared/components/ui`, `lib` → `@/core/lib`, `composables` → `@/core/composables`.

## Conventions

- Vue components in PascalCase; composables with `use` prefix.
- New feature: add a new folder under `src/modules/<name>/` with `model/` (and `view/` if it has a page); register the route in `core/router/index.ts` and lazy-import the view from `@/modules/<name>/view/...`.
- Auth: `useAuthStore` from `@/modules/auth/model/store`; routes use `meta.requiresAuth` and `meta.public`.
- Theme: `initTheme()` from `@/core/composables/useTheme` in `main.ts`.
- New UI primitives: add via shadcn-vue (components.json) so they go to `shared/components/ui/`.
- Env: `VITE_API_URL` for the API (see `env.d.ts` and `.env.example`).

## Scripts

- `pnpm dev` — development
- `pnpm build` — type-check + build
- `pnpm lint` — ESLint with fix
- `pnpm format` — Prettier on `src/`
